2u-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%AD-Do-nh%E1%BB%8B-tuy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-t18QFUswKz7lnO4yVtj64A">Sơ đáo Hàng Châu ký Tử Do nhị tuyệt kỳ 1 - 初到杭州寄子由二絕其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-tr%E1%BA%ADn-vong/poem-JnHWJb5Kd6-M07NFz1l5Zw">Tế trận vong - 祭陣亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-FosXAk5Cd82BSMJXLASuig">Thị tịch - 示寂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ns4tI6tkcr_BjJ8gp7Etow">Tịnh Giới thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-L%E1%BB%87nh-C%E1%BB%AD-ai-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-nouAchrrbZE2Ttq8F3suBg">Trần Lệnh Cử ai từ - 陳令舉哀詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-P6xtQk8fCZudef4S0B9eeQ">Ức tích kỳ 2 - 憶昔其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
